the sumador chino.won a recent motor trip through mexico, the writercame across on adding device which was referred to as a sumador chino (chinese adder).  a survey of the moreavailable literature on the history of mathematics and on instruments of calculation has uncovered no referenceto such a device.  the purpose of this communication is to enlist the help of other members in bringing tolight whatever may be known concerning the evolution and present status of the sumador chino.cacm november, rogers, j. l.ca jb march ,   : pm